experiences.detail:
SPE is the largest non-profit association serving managers, engineers, scientists and other professionals worldwide in the oil and gas industry.
Achievements/Tasks Organised the annual biggest sport fundraising event in the Oil & Gas industry - SPE Golf & Tennis Tournament 2015 in Vung Tau with
1,500 participants. Total fundraising value: USD$ 0.5 million in 3 days;
Coordinated monthly technical workshops and continuing education courses with distinguished lecturers in the industry for SPE members and non-members;
Implemented charity projects including bicycle donation to 120 poor pupils in BVT, heart operations to 20 children, 03 book donation campaigns, 01 kindergarten & 01 library sponsorship in Tra Vinh.

Dentsu Inc. is a Japanese international advertising and public relations joint stock company headquartered in Tokyo. Achievements/Tasks Supervised and followed-up media buying contracts and invoices of multiple channels (TV, print, OOH, digital);
Monitored print-ads by tracking deadlines and publication specifications:
Managed the daily work flow of client campaigns, including proposal development, campaign activation maintenance, and post-campaign reporting;
Organised the sport event “Watch AFF Cup with Suzuki” in November 2014 for 16,000 participants at Military Zone 7 Stadium.
